				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Juwel wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">So far in the groups I've been in (all guildies) every time they've grouped with me for the first time someone has said at some point of the evening. "Enchanters ROCK!" 
